<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Your certificate is ready</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f5f5f5; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1a1a1a; }
    .wrapper { padding: 40px 16px; }
    .container { background-color: #ffffff; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; overflow: hidden; }
    .body { padding: 40px 40px 32px; }
    h1 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 16px; color: #111111; }
    p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 24px; color: #444444; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #111111; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 5px; }
    .footer { padding: 20px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee; }
    .footer p { font-size: 12px; color: #999999; margin: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="body">
        <h1>Your certificate is ready</h1>
        <p>Hi <strong><%= recipientName %></strong>,</p>
        <p>Your certificate has been issued by <strong><%= orgName %></strong> and recorded on the blockchain.</p>
        <p>You can verify the authenticity of your certificate at any time using the link below.</p>
        <a href="<%= verificationUrl %>" class="btn">Verify Certificate</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>If you have any questions, please contact the issuing organisation directly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
